                  <Text layoutX="76.0" layoutY="301.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="C was developed in the early 1970s by Dennis Ritchie at AT&amp;T Bell Laboratories." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
