                  <Text layoutX="76.0" layoutY="918.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="– C++ programs contain one or more functions, exactly one ofwhich must be main" textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
