                  <Text layoutX="76.0" layoutY="960.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="– int means that main &quot;returns&quot; an integer value" textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
