                     </font>
                  </Text>
                  <Text layoutX="76.0" layoutY="981.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="– Braces ({ and }) indicate a block• The bodies of all functions must be contained in braces" textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
